mmediately."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Serve with bite-sized pieces of bread, which you can dip into fondue with fondue forks.","Instead of bread, you can serve with french fries or vegetables (e.g. cauliflower, broccoli or asparagus).","Always use good drinking wine when adding to your fondue.","If you prefer, omit Kirsch from the fondue. Invite guests who enjoy Kirsch to lightly dip skewered bread into a glass of Kirsch before dipping into the fondue pot.","When using an aged Gruyère cheese mix each batch of Gruyère cheese an additional 10 sec\/speed 7 to make sure cheese is well chopped.","Replace Kirsch with steamed pears and pear liqueur.","Before serving, add fresh tomatoes and basil."],"basicInfo":["medium","5m","15m","6 portions"]}